Package sandra.libs.dm.formfilllib

Class Summary
DialogInterpreter Dialog manager that follows a form-filling approach
Field Represents a field in a dialogue.
Form Represents a form containing a dialogue.
VXMLParser Parser that processes the contents of a VXML file and creates a Form object with a collection of Field objects.
 

Exception Summary
FormFillLibException Exception to account for the problems that may appear in the FormFillLib.
